headline.main: US Sen. Warren Turns Fundraising Powerhouse for Democrats
headline.print_headline: US Sen. Warren Turns Fundraising Powerhouse for Democrats

lead_paragraph: At the core of Massachusetts Sen. Elizabeth Warren's appeal is a critique of an economic system she says is rigged against the little guy.
